      "body": "Since HTTP Structured Headers ([draft-ietf-httpbis-header-structure](https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-httpbis-header-structure)) are nearing publication, we should turn `DoH-Preference` into an Item Structured Header.",
      "createdAt": "2020-02-25T20:00:19Z",
      "updatedAt": "2020-02-25T20:00:19Z",
